details.name: Flak Cannon
details.description: Gyrocopter's attacks hit all enemy units in an area around it for a limited number of attacks.  Only the main target of attacks will receive attack bonuses such as Critical Strike.  Lasts 15/15/15/15 seconds or until the attacks are used.
details.upgrade_description: Adds a Side Gunner that at random attacks enemy units near Gyrocopter.
